Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Hi, everybody, my name is Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:10.58,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Ah... otherwise known as Britjet on PSX forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:14.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I'm a retired BA(British Airways) 747 pilot and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.84,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,playing with PSX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:20.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,but I am not sure that's the right word, because it's so realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,certainly got me hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:26.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And I thought I put together, some videos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,showing some aspects of the operation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:31.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the 747 which might not be immediately obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:34.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in various manuals you can get you hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Health warning:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,any pros watching this trying to glean some information\Nfor your next check
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:42.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please don't, just use your own SOPs and your knowledges
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's equally as good as mine if not much better
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This is just for fun, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:51.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This particular approach is, e...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,onto 27L Heathrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,all LOC on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And ATCs are gonna tell us or ask us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.08,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to go for 27R.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,There are also some bottom lines to this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Don't do it in bad weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:07.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you couldn't be able to see the other runway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And don't trying do this below 2000ft
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:13.97,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You're gonna run out of time \N to get everything sort for a nice approach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:18.02,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,[C] Taking glass aspect of this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,of that, on the 747
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:24.08,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Once glide slop is captured like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:28.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the basic flying modes on the MCP are locked out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to save your messing up the approach with finger trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:35.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So Altitude HLD, V/S, Heading HLD, FLCH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:37.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,they don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:38.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Similarly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you can't select another ILS frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So if I go to depart the arrival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,trying select another ILS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You CAN'T
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:50.24,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Again, it's stop for finger trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The other thing I like you to bear in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,it's the ALT SEL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Now the ALT SEL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,doesn't do anything once the glideslop is captured
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:01.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,[C] again, nuts to deliberate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.97,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If we gonna take that glideslop out of some stage, however
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.74,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the ALT SEL becomes alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:09.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and you can get seriously in the  way of further approach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.58,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:13.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,how we gonna get from 27L to 27R
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,or you could fly Go-Around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.57,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,tell ATC that you stuff it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.57,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Or we can say, well, it's a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:23.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,we got time, let's go 27R.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,[C] You ought to take out the automatics
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:29.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you can't reprogram at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You can take them out\Nand just throw it on the other runway visually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's on way, a bit messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Or the way I'm gonna show you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:40.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,is......\NPutting the automatic back in,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,get everything sorted so that is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,nice and stable by a thousand feet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.46,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,while the check is done
